Actor Duro Michael has received financial help from, Senior Prophet Jeremiah Omoto Fufeyin, the founder and head Prophet of Christ Mercy Land Deliverance Ministry, Warri, Delta State. The veteran actor recently cried out for assistance to replace his amputated leg with an artificial one. Michael had battled diabetes for a long time, which led to the amputation of his right leg as a result of complications in order to preserve his life. In the viral video where the actor solicited help, he sat down on a chair in front of his house and said: “I greet you all, my brothers and sister. You have seen it. It was caused by diabetes.   Ex-BBNaija Tochi proposes to US-based girlfriend     Why I sent Sandra Iheuwa packing five months after wedding,…     Banky W: I was rich but felt empty, struggled with…   - Advertisement - “So, I plead with you all, in whatever way you can help me, please do. So I can get an artificial leg so that I can be happy. God bless you as you help me, Amen! “I’m still that your person, Duro Michael, your guy. I’m still the man I used to be. I haven’t changed. God bless you. Prophet Fufeyin saw the video and sent emissaries to go seek out the actor. The prophet inquired from the actor what he needed and the latter revealed he needed an artificial leg seeing he’s an amputee so he could walk like other people. He noted the leg was amputated on June 4, 2021, and he needed N600,000 to acquire an artificial one. Fufeyin prayed for him and revealed he hasn’t sent the sum of N5million naira to cater for the acquisition of an artificial leg and his family’s needs.